</B></color>Cortilizers once occupied most of the world\'s territory, and humans could only survive in the city-state. It was called the Old Calendar at that time.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>New Calendar:</size></B></color>The new calendar, which is the first year when humans began to launch a full-scale counterattack against corrupters, corresponds to the old calendar.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>City-State:</size></B></color>The stronghold established by humans in the old calendar to gather together for warmth, and after the new calendar, it became the most technologically developed civilization center. There are currently nine city-State in the world.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Camp:</size></B></color>A loose organization formed by birds of a feather flocks to the group and for the purpose of mutual benefit does not have any binding force in itself.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Qimingxing Technology:</size></B></color>High-tech enterprises with the highest level of research on X energy can even improve energy utilization efficiency through technical means.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Guardian:</size></B></color>The technological product of the mechanical camp is a good helper for traveling at home in the wilderness.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Pioneer:</size></B></color>The by-product of the magic camp\'s research on gods can use the power of the corresponding gods to a certain extent through mysterious means.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Warship:</size></B></color>The earliest airship was used to deliver supplies to adventurers in the wilderness. With the advancement of technology, it also had the ability to deliver firepower and opened up related businesses.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>The Battle of Supernatural Powers:</size></B></color>Since the new calendar, conflicts within human beings have increased, so the Battle of Supernatural Powers has emerged as a system for arbitration, and the rule is that winners take all.','<color=#FFD12B><B><size=40>Rel