 be wasted!','Nuwa|After a long time of training, you have finally become a qualified <color=#a23cf0>Divine Friendship</color>~','1|Finally received recognition from the goddess! But what special abilities does the <color=#a23cf0>Divine Respect</color> have?','Nuwa|<color=#a23cf0>The God-Follower</color> is more than one title. The real God-Follower</color> can help the team members fight with the help of the powerful gene.','1|Did I say... As the protagonist, can I finally <color=#a23cf0> go to the battle</color>? Take me to see it!','Nuwa| Here you can view your status, upgrade yourself and configure the <color=#a23cf0>gene</color>. The gods can release powerful skills in battle by configuring the <color=#a23cf0>gene with various divine powers.','Nuwa|<color=#a23cf0>gene</color> can be obtained through <color=#a23cf0>gene research</color>, and I have given you a <color=#a23cf0>blueprint</color> for genetic research.','Nuwa | The foundation of the gods and genes has been told, but as the new gods, you still need to continuously improve your level in order to unlock more <color=#a23cf0>gene columns</color>, and you can become powerful by obtaining a stronger <color=#a23cf0>gene</color>.','1|I used to be just watching the game, but now it\'s finally my turn. I can\'t wait!','Log in <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Give friends and friendship points <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Headhunting company recruits <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Participate in <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times of material collection','Accept the <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> exploration task','Quick training <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Underground Arena Challenge <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Challenge Guild Copy <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> times','Make <color=#FFD12B><size=36><b>%s</b></size></color> 